Determine whether the following homogeneous linear systems have nontrivial solutions. If so, give the general solution.

$$
\left\{
\begin{aligned}
3x_1-5x_2+x_3-2x_4&=0\\
2x_1+3x_2-5x_3+x_4&=0\\
-x_1+7x_2-4x_3+3x_4&=0\\
4x_1+15x_2-7x_3+9x_4&=0
\end{aligned}
\right.
$$

$$
\left\{
\begin{aligned}
5x_1-2x_2+4x_3-3x_4&=0\\
-3x_1+5x_2-x_3+2x_4&=0\\
x_1-3x_2+2x_3+x_4&=0
\end{aligned}
\right.
$$
